{"tid":479153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登成功改變世界，當年奶共高登一台獨大，大時大節必定熄燈","createTime":"2017-11-24T18:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T06:53:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b77d860c93762ed0907322beadfd9f88c0ee8c1a","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"如果當年唔係有膠登我肯定雨傘革命高登一定熄燈，大家居然以為林狗真係咁偉大唔熄燈，佢係怕畀人搶生意咋"},{"pid":"3e817830dff60a0dea6c92feab8b51b1c026f4ef","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"想當年上高登慘過食兩舊屎，每十分鐘先load到一個post，一台獨大又可以亂ban人無需理由，就算連登真係某啲人講到咁垃圾，起碼佢打破到一台獨大先"},{"pid":"be9e7d20f2d87fb6355b7200c5daac03b15ecca6","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T19:10:57.000Z","msg":"啲人洗晒腦盲目話嗰啲係「書面語」真係喊出嚟  <br />\n根本係粵文書寫嘅權利被剝削，反而仲畀人話「口語」嘛，「連『書面語』都唔識返去讀過小一」 ，過幾年就有細路話我地講嘅廣東話係「市井語」，出街買嘢傾計緊係用普通話啦，連「普通話」都唔識返去讀小一。 <br />\n好多廣東話根本唔係唔寫得出嚟唔體面，但就因為有「書面語」概念，盲目用咗某啲廣東話唔用嘅字同文法，依啲已經唔係書唔書面問題啦。 <br />\n最慘嘅係支持「書面語」嘅都係啲老一輩專家，新一代撐粵文嘅就被人覺得唔夠料，依家仲要精英班用普通話"},{"pid":"bd7db5ca636f7158c1efd337a57282c432999a3d","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T20:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18ef9457bb9e6e8a3aeaacd46fca0c097a8e016","tid":479153,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T20:45:55.000Z","msg":"有競爭先有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一可惜連登問題未解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dd872154ff26b5d0c49617edfce469b9338654","tid":479153,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T20:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有競爭先有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一可惜連登<span style=\"color: red;\">五毛</span>問題未解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼訓打漏字sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近有BAM五毛值得一讚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ef3881aca2105f9d70e0157973a0c036079802","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T22:09:46.000Z","msg":"d 人係跟住個app 黎行. 用慣左HKG+ 既速度, 你好難用其他app 而速度同介面係跟唔上. 由其官方IOS 個app, 夜晚多人個時, 係每睇3個post 就斷一次線. 開個post 睇等30秒. 你係用唔到個官方app. <br />\n<br />\n比個參考你, HKG+ 篤落一個post 睇係秒開, 回post 就要等7~8秒. 而家LIHKG 係秒開秒回. 速度係接近Whatsapp 睇野同回覆既速度."},{"pid":"a0f669c4f1ec74df58dbe69a07838c8a820d1a06","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T23:01:53.000Z","msg":"膠登比較小圈子feel <br />\n上左左陣個感覺喺嗰度啲人已經大家都認得大家 好難融入<br />\n同埋又有班老屎忽會話人當膠登condom<br />\n有啲人上一排quit左 之後再返黎 又會比人鬧<br />\n感覺上唔係613註冊/一路上開就係二等公民<br />\n<br />\n其實上forum都係求開心/搵個平台傾偈姐<br />\n見到膠登咁樣<br />\n邊個會想上"},{"pid":"caf7d889bbc5efa0162feec1c7f7969489141099","tid":479153,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0141e107e3fabf50da03f92ba61ce0d0fecc4d2","tid":479153,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"支爆未?"},{"pid":"6a6955028c8ff32ac67fcae18180e1bd6ea724fb","tid":479153,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持百花齊放<br />\n<br />\n一台獨大好危險, 攪掂一個就得。"},{"pid":"56be9265aff9dcd9e3d081f08ddbf96cf28950db","tid":479153,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"今晚 19:01 連登開壇一週年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1990669b4e966e873a8